  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(This may be cast with your <strong>Phoenix Talon Hijutsu</strong> instead of a weapon)</em> You focus your blazing chakra within your weapon or Claws causing them to ignite with beautiful multi-colored flames before delivering a devastating attack. This jutsu does not cost any additional chakra while concentrating. Starting next turn, you can spend your Action to slash, igniting the air around you in a majestic display. All creatures within a 30 feet long, 15ft wide horizontal line must make a Constitution saving throw or take 4d6 Fire and 4d6 Slashing damage or half as much on a success as the area detonates with multiple explosions seemingly appearing as if multiple solar eclipses are occurring at the same time. This jutsu only ends upon use. If a creature fails by more than 5 of the DC, they instead take maximum damage. This Jutsu ignites flammable objects that aren't being worn or carried.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For every rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, increase both the fire and slashing damage dealt by an additional 1d6 for each rank above C-Rank.</p>",
